TI  - Bta-miR-493 Inhibits Bovine Preadipocytes Differentiation by Targeting BMPR1A via the TGFβ/BMP and p38MAPK Signaling Pathways
PY  - 2022
T2  - Journal of Agricultural and Food Chemistry
VL  - 70
IS  - 46
SP  - 14641
