TI  - Targeted overexpression of PPARγ in skeletal muscle by random insertion and CRISPR/Cas9 transgenic pig cloning enhances oxidative fiber formation and intramuscular fat deposition
PY  - 2021
T2  - FASEB Journal
VL  - 35
IS  - 2
