TI  - Unveiling Conserved Molecular Pathways of Intramuscular Fat Deposition and Shared Metabolic Processes in Semitendinosus Muscle of Hereford, Holstein, and Limousine Cattle via RNA-Seq Analysis
PY  - 2025
