TI  - Integration of ATAC-Seq and RNA-Seq Reveals VDR–SELENBP1 Axis Promotes Adipogenesis of Porcine Intramuscular Preadipocytes
PY  - 2024
T2  - International Journal of Molecular Sciences
VL  - 25
IS  - 23
